<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-row>
      <ProductComp class="col-3" :card="product" v-for="product in products" :key="product.id"/>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>

import ProductComp from "@/components/ProductComp.vue";

export default {
  name: "ProductsView",
  components: {ProductComp},
  computed: {
    products() {
      return this.$store.state.products;
    },
  },
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>

</style>
